::Killfest/Scyther::

Killfest listens to Lunarpine&#39;s transmission, frowning and forming a plan in his mind. He looks at Shivah. &quot;Don&#39;t answer that comm yet.&quot;

The commander looks over his left shoulder. &quot;Scyther.&quot; His spy slowly materializes to the left of him, looking at him and ready for orders. He&#39;d already predicted half of Killfest&#39;s plan.

&quot;Yes?&quot;

Without answering Scyther, Killfest looks over at Shivah. &quot;Is there any way to leave the base right now?&quot; he asks, &quot;I&#39;m going to send Scyther out to scout. He&#39;ll be undetectable. Meanwhile, you set up a transmission blocker to block everything but yours and that Maximal&#39;s transmissions. We capture the two inside, if he&#39;s lying and they&#39;re really inside, and hold them for &#39;negotiations&#39;. Scyther will determine if the one outside is alone. If yes, he can kill him or capture him. Meanwhile, have your troops search for any bombs in the base while you keep talking and distracting him.&quot;

He waits for Shivah&#39;s opinion. To him, it was a good plan.




